dct_description_sm: California as an island with indented coastline, and with place names R. d Estiete, C. Blanca, P. de Carinda, Canal de Sta. Barbe, I. de S. Martin, B. de S. Francisco, I. de S. marc, B. de S. Simon, B. S. Christoual, and Bernabe.
Title cartouche with 3 palm trees and 2 seated natives (top left).
Copied by or from La Feuille.
Engraved by: M. Ogier fecit (bottom left).
